{"tid":2332754,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜濤恨拍拖走出A0 封60歲紅姑做夢中女神","createTime":"2020-12-20T00:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T04:13:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8d432af7f6d5e3bcc388b57769d7793311cc7c54","tid":2332754,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T00:22:41.000Z","msg":"比起大台的人力財力，ViuTV的真人騷《全民造星》系列，絕對是近年低成本高效益的上佳之作。今年來到第三屆，話題依然源源不絕。正當焦點落在10強人選時，身為元祖級的姜濤，在這兩年默默耕耘下，無論在歌、視領域已邁向「造星」之路，去年商台頒獎禮還是拿生力軍銅奬，今年已成功殺入我最喜愛男歌手5強，速度之快如坐火箭。不過賽果未揭曉，姜濤早已心裏有數。日前他接受《蘋果》訪問時坦言：「入到5強都係fans投我一票，會珍惜但唔會因為咁沖昏頭腦，事實係打定輸數，因為自己資歷唔係咁勁，咪以為入到5強就有5強嘅實力，不過呢個係一個好好機會，等大家認識有個叫姜濤嘅人，可以聽吓佢啲歌！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201220/BSSSITGKN5H6TPAUKMVCN5TRP4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201220%2FBSSSITGKN5H6TPAUKMVCN5TRP4%2F&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWFDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=107201b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201220%2FBSSSITGKN5H6TPAUKMVCN5TRP4%2F&h=1cdb0481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201220/BSSSITGKN5H6TPAUKMVCN5TRP4/</a>"},{"pid":"75d67a8765349b6d065a62dea8686f16d76be81c","tid":2332754,"uid":109850,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T00:30:22.000Z","msg":"呀姨 我不想努力了"},{"pid":"ac382015c91c502013b2174c0469fe98cdb6ecb7","tid":2332754,"uid":214580,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T00:52:10.000Z","msg":"A0邊個信"},{"pid":"4c08359cbd94c1cd4d9ff7716439ff4b3f433de5","tid":2332754,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"ac382015c91c502013b2174c0469fe98cdb6ecb7","tid":2332754,"uid":214580,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T00:52:10.000Z","msg":"A0邊個信"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T00:53:05.000Z","msg":"破處唔等於拍拖。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7